		<description><![CDATA[Learn practical and useful vocabulary about buying food in a supermarket in China. Learn names of the food products that we cannot live without, like bread, butter, milk, yoghurt, cheese, eggs, meat etc. Living in China can be tough if you can&#8217;t find the food you are used to. And after all, it&#8217;s much safer [...]]]></description>
