				<category><![CDATA[Lessons]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.melnyks.com/lesson-098-funeral/</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[This lesson will teach you expressions in Mandarin Chinese related to death, funeral, expressing condolences etc. You will also learn a bunch of other useful vocabulary and sentence patterns in Mandarin Chinese. So download your Mp3 file, open a transcript and start learning!]]></description>
